data.description: LOCATION... LOCATION... LOCATION!!! This custom build home has it all. BRAND NEW ROOF, huge saltwater pool added in 2020, all windows and doors are impact resistant, quartz counter tops, soft close drawers and cabinets in the kitchen. Matching quartz counter tops and high end finishes in both bathrooms. The backyard has a pergola and large area by the pool to entertain your guests. Fine dining, shopping, world class fishing, boating and nightlife are all nearby!!
